inalog [Grant 2023-1-307TKI]. Some of this work has been executed under the TKI Dinalog [Grant 2023-1-307TKI]. Part of this work was completed during a research visit made possible by a [Distinguished Visitor Award] from the University of Auckland.Supplemental Material: The online appendix and data files are available at https://doi.org/10.1287/mnsc.2022.04024.
