T1  - Model-Free Nonstationary Reinforcement Learning: Near-Optimal Regret and Applications in Multiagent Reinforcement Learning and Inventory Control
AU  - Mao, Weichao
AU  - Zhang, Kaiqing
AU  - Zhu, Ruihao
AU  - Simchi-Levi, David
AU  - Başar, Tamer
Y1  - 2024/05/14
PY  - 2024
